Job Details - L&D; Director - Retail
L&D; Director - Retail
Maandag 5 mei 2014
Description
Digby Morgan are currently recruiting for an exciting opportunity, based in Dubai, for an L&D; Director to cover the retail side of a diversified local business.The successful applicant will be required to vision and strategically plan the whole L&D; function for this fantastic company.You must be familiar with the 70,20,10 theory and have the ability to apply this to the L&D; plan for the business. Experience building Academies and Graduate Schemes is a big part of the role.For this role you must have a proven background within a similar role and also speak Arabic as well as English.
Regional experience is also a must to take on this role. Relevant qualifications within L&D; will be required.}
Job Reference:RJMW015812
Position Type:Permanent
Sector:Human Resources, Retail/Wholesale
Job Duration:n/a
Working Hours:Full-time
Location:Dubai, United Arab Emirates
Salary:£130,000 - £160,000 per year
Contact:Rebecca Morecroft, Contact Code: PO Box 125115, Digby Morgan, Digby Morgan (DIFC) Limited, United Arab Emirates
Phone / Fax:971 (0) 4 401 9196 / 44 (0)20 7495 4474
